\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\fi566\s28\sl240\slmult1\itap0{\s28\f0\fs24\b\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Quick description: }{\s28\f0\fs24\lang1033{\*\listtag0}LangGenerator is a program that generates files based on a grammar input file. The program fully supports EBNF and regex like syntax: \{\}, [], (), ?, +, *. Basically it generates possible implementations of that grammar.}{\s28\f0\fs24\b\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
